"ÔÖº ALT E" "Rofi Emoticons" "Emoticon" \
"ÔÖº ALT V" "Clipboard Manager" "cliphist" \
"ÔÖº H" "Launch this app" "" \
"ÔÖº E" "View or EDIT Keybinds, Settings, Monitor" "" \
"" "" "" \
